PRODUCTS.name: A Day at the Beach
PRODUCTS.description: You can practically hear the waves crashing and almost feel a gentle breeze caressing your face. This bounty of nature’s beauty boasts green roses, blue delphinium, pink Asiatic lilies, Bell of Ireland and lily grass in an elegant clear cylinder vase.

PRODUCTS.name: A Day In the Sun
PRODUCTS.description: This striking bouquet of pink and orange roses with yellow alstroemeria in a green bud vase will leave her beaming with joy.

PRODUCTS.name: All Orange For You
PRODUCTS.description: Rejoice in the colorful accents of fall with this dramatic grouping of orange asiatic lilies and roses  in a simple clear rose vase, giving an overall impressive look!

PRODUCTS.name: Best Wishes Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: Red carnations, yellow daisies, purple Monte Casino blooms and green button poms in a clear fluted vase with a colorful curly ribbon. Put it all together and you’re sure to make someone’s wishes come true!

PRODUCTS.name: Blooming Meadow Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: Transport yourself to a quiet morning as the sun splashes its rays on a peaceful meadow. That's the feeling this bouquet creates as sunflowers, roses, alstroemeria, carnations, fuji, delphinium and solidago are arranged in clear swirl vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Blooms of Beauty
PRODUCTS.description: Make their birthday or everyday occasion extra special with this sweet poppy bouquet of gerberas, hypericum, stock and bells of Ireland in a clear gathering vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Blue & White Brilliance
PRODUCTS.description: A vivacious, sparkling combination of beautiful blooms makes this bouquet a brilliant choice for almost any celebratory occasion! Alstroemeria, carnations, roses, delphinium and waxflower are skillfully blended in a clear gathering vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Bountiful Impressions
PRODUCTS.description: Bountiful indeed! There’s a whole lot to love about this fantastic arrangement including sunflowers, purple statice, hot pink gerbera daisies, orange and pink roses, pink waxflower and green athos in a great-looking glass cylinder container.

PRODUCTS.name: Bright Blue Skies Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: The gorgeous white Asiatic lilies grab your attention right away, but they only begin to tell the story of this uniquely beautiful bouquet also boasting yellow roses, light blue delphinium and purple Monte Casino blooms...all creatively arranged in a clear rose vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Brightest Memories
PRODUCTS.description: Brilliantly colorful, this collection of yellow Asiatic lilies, white roses and yellow alstroemeria in a clear urn vase is sure to make a wide array of remembrances shine bright. Complementing the look is a gracious white satin ribbon.

PRODUCTS.name: Brilliance Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: Brilliant colors, brilliant choice. Green poms, purple alstroemeria, hot pink gerberas, orange roses and yellow daisies literally shine in all their glory, accented by a bright green container.

PRODUCTS.name: Cherished Moments
PRODUCTS.description: Show them how much you cherish having them in your life by giving this spectacular gift of regal roses, cheerful daisies, delicate stock and graceful bells of Ireland all gathered in a beautiful green swirl vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Country Sunshine
PRODUCTS.description: Add some cheer to their day with this charming bouquet of fresh roses, Viking poms, heather and hypericum arranged in a yellow bud vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Daisy a Day Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: Somehow, the color yellow has a way of instantly creating a smile on just about anyone’s face. Yellow gerbera and yellow alstroemeria are definitely the focal points of this arrangement, which also features white poms and white Monte Casino blooms in a clear rose vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Daisy Celebration
PRODUCTS.description: Admit it, daisies have that certain look, that look of happiness along with a bold expression of personality. This botanical celebration accentuates all those thoughts, showcasing white daisies in a yellow cache container featuring floral accents.

PRODUCTS.name: Daisy Delight
PRODUCTS.description: Send this spectacular bouquet of daisies, roses, carnations and statice in a clear swirl vase.  It's sure to delight the senses and it's perfect for celebrating any occasion with style.

PRODUCTS.name: Enchanting Moments Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: You share all kinds of special moments with Mom, now share this wondrous bouquet crafted with yellow roses, purple aster and magenta carnations in a swirl purple vase.

PRODUCTS.name: European Garden Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: You’ll feel like you’ve been transported to the peace and tranquility of an actual garden when you see and smell this wonderful combination of alstroemeria, button poms, Monte Casino, sunflowers, roses and Asiatic lilies in a clear rose vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Simple Charm Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: The essence of Europe comes to life in all its grandeur with this bright assortment of alstroemeria, button poms, Monte casino, sunflowers and tulips in an elegant clear rose vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Everyday Elegance Bouquet - Pink
PRODUCTS.description: When this bouquet arrives, your fortunate recipient will undoubtedly think that dreams do come true. White gerbera daises, red roses, pink lilies, white spray roses and pink waxflower adorn a stylish pink fluted vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Feelin' Good
PRODUCTS.description: You'll have them feelin' good when you send this striking bouquet of hot pink gerberas, orange carnations and purple statice in a classic clear gathering vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Fields of Sunshine
PRODUCTS.description: Celebrate the beauty of the season with this stunning gathering of roses, daisy poms, lilies and delphinium expertly designed in a cobalt gathering vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Fiery Fall Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: Fall is a season unlike any other, bursting forth with a kaleidoscope of glowing color. This innovative bouquet captures the colorful expressions of fall...showcasing sunflowers, roses, button poms, carnations, yarrow, statice and hypericum in a lovely gathering vase.

PRODUCTS.name: Floral Artisan Bouquet
PRODUCTS.description: Express your thoughts and deliver an ear-to-ear  smile to that special someone. This artisnal bouquet boasts Asiatic lilies, roses, button poms, mini carnations and sunflowers in a graceful gathering vase...ideal  for saying thank you, get well, happy Administrative Professionals Day, or just about any other occasion.
